comments.body:
@dm17 We don't support that from what I can see, but I'll let @QiWang19 correct me if I'm mistaken.
I'm going to change the title of this issue and make it a request to add the functionality.  It looks like it would be doable.

For a quick thumbnail sketch, this is requesting adding the `--ignore/-i` option to the build command which would allow the user to specify a particular `.dockerignore` file to use rather than the default.
